# TOTO List

- The repository TOTO list lives in `docs/TOTO.md`.
- Update that file only when the user explicitly asks to add, change, or close a TOTO item.
- Do not treat every `TODO` mention in chat or code as an instruction to edit the TOTO file.
- Preserve the existing Markdown table structure.
- When adding an item, use the next sequential number and the current date in `YYYY-MM-DD` format.
